OL,5, A seven-year-old boy who is campaigning
OL,6, to replace single-use water bottles in 
OL,7, school lunchboxes has been invited to  
OL,8, COP26.                                 
OL,10,FCallum Isted wants all primary children
OL,11,Fin Scotland to have a reusable bottle  
OL,12,Fand access to taps where they can      
OL,13,Frefill them at school.                 
OL,15,FHe completed the John Muir Way in      
OL,16,Fstages to raise #1,400 to buy steel    
OL,17,Fbottles for all pupils at his school.  
OL,19,FThey were previously given single use  
OL,20,Fbottles with a packed lunch on Fridays.
